Changelogs.

1.0

  First demo version of OpenCreative+.
  - Added flat world generation.
  - Added worlds browser menu.

  2022

1.1 

  Second demo version of OpenCreative+. Not stable.
  - Added global chat (/cc).
  - Added world's settings (name, description, icon)

  2022

1.2
 
  Fixed version of 1.1.
  2023

1.3 - You like translating plugins, don't you?

  Third demo version of OpenCreative+.
  - Added customizable messages.
  - Added new commands and menus.  
  - Begin of development mode (/dev).
  2023

1.4 - Keep your friends close.

  First release version of OpenCreative+.
  - Added development mode (/dev) with few coding blocks.
  - Added players management (kick, ban)
  2024

5.0 - Things will be different.

  Second release version of OpenCreative+. Most stable and powerful.
  - Improved development mode (/dev) with platforms customization.
  - Added a lot of coding blocks.
  - Added conditions.
  - Added NOT arrow, block mover items.
  - Added variables (local, global, saved).
  - Added new values (Number, Location, Boolean, Variable...).
  - Changed menus.
  2024

5.1 - Well, it's possiblle.
  
  - Added requirements in config
  - Added custom heads, banners support for world icons
  - Fixed issues
  2025

5.2 - Well, it's possible.
  
  - Duplicated 30 player actions as 30 entity actions
  - Added new player event
  - Added new world action 
  2025

5.3 - Well, it's possible.
 
  - Changed /unloadedWorlds/ to /planets/
  - Now worlds don't move between world container and planets folders 
  - New entities browser menu
  - New requirements in config.yml
  - Added /like and /ad costs in config.yml
  2025

5.3.1 - Well, it's possible.

  - Fixed kill potions issue
  2025

5.4 - Well, it's possible.

  - Added moderation menu
  - Added world access menu
  - Added customizable sounds in config.yml
  2025

5.4.1 - Well, it's possible.

  - Added new environment and world subcommands
  - Default sign is Birch instead of Oak
  2025

5.4.2 - Well, it's possible.

  - Added %list(name, index) placeholder
  2025

5.4.3 - Well, it's possible.
 
  - Fixed selection action issues
  2025

5.5 - Well, it's possible.

  - Added 32 entity events
  - Added 35 world events
  - Added 2 player events
  - Added 3 player actions
  2025
  
5.5.1 - Well, it's possible.

  - Fixed custom containers issue
  - Fixed platforms issue
  2025

5.6 - Well, it's possible.

  - Added repeat and controller coding blocks
  - Added %event% placeholder
  - Added 4 repeat actions
  - Added 2 controller actions
  - Added 1 entity conditions
  - Added 9 entity actions
  - Added 1 player action
  - Added 4 world actions
  - Added 1 control action
  - Added physical objects by pawsashatoy
  - Added world's whitelist
  - Added /oc register and /oc unregister commands
  - Added bad items fixer
  - Added lobby permissions for player groups
  - Added disabling coding blocks in config.yml
  2025

5.7 - Well, it's possible

  - :-)
  
